Up-to-date installation instructions for Schemix can always be found at:
http://www.schemix.org/install.html

If your system is well-configured already (kernel source installed and
configured, etc.) you should just be able to do:

$ cd /usr/src/linux
$ make SUBDIRS=/path/to/schemix/ modules
$ make SUBDIRS=/path/to/schemix/ modules_install
